Igor Clark <igor+gen_serial@igorclark.net>

Added basic rebar support for the POSIX build in January 2019.


Tom Szilagyi <tomszilagyi@gmail.com>:

Released 0.2 in July 2014 with a backend driver added for POSIX (Linux
and UNIX-like) operating systems along with small fixes.


Shawn Pearce <spearce+erlang@spearce.org>:

Original author of gen_serial; released 0.1 in February 2004 with the
general Erlang API and a Windows backend driver in place.
